msgid "Accountant"
msgstr "นักบัญชี"

msgid "Accountant Job Duties: Prepares asset, liability, and capital account entries by compiling and analyzing account information. Documents financial transactions by entering account information. Recommends financial actions by analyzing accounting options. Summarizes current financial status by collecting information; preparing balance sheet, profit and loss statement, and other reports. Substantiates financial transactions by auditing documents. Maintains accounting controls by preparing and recommending policies and procedures. Guides accounting clerical staff by coordinating activities and answering questions. Reconciles financial discrepancies by collecting and analyzing account information. Secures financial information by completing data base backups. Maintains financial security by following internal controls. Prepares payments by verifying documentation, and requesting disbursements. Answers accounting procedure questions by researching and interpreting accounting policy and regulations. Complies with federal, state, and local financial legal requirements by studying existing and new legislation, enforcing adherence to requirements, and advising management on needed actions. Prepares special financial reports by collecting, analyzing, and summarizing account information and trends. Maintains customer confidence and protects operations by keeping financial information confidential. Maintains professional and technical knowledge by attending educational workshops; reviewing professional publications; establishing personal networks; participating in professional societies. Accomplishes the result by performing the duty. Contributes to team effort by accomplishing related results as needed."
msgstr "Accountant งาน Duties: Prepares asset, liability, และ capital account entries ตาม compiling และ analyzing account information. Documents financial transactions ตาม entering account information. Recommends financial actions ตาม analyzing accounting options. Summarizes current financial สถานะ ตาม collecting information; preparing balance sheet, profit และ loss statement, และ other reports. Substantiates financial transactions ตาม auditing documents. Maintains accounting controls ตาม preparing และ recommending policies และ procedures. Guides accounting clerical staff ตาม coordinating activities และ answering questions. Reconciles financial discrepancies ตาม collecting และ analyzing account information. Secures financial information ตาม completing data base backups. Maintains financial security ตาม following internal controls. Prepares payments ตาม verifying documentation, และ requesting disbursements. Answers accounting procedure questions ตาม reค้นหาing และ interpreting accounting policy และ regulations. Complies ด้วย federal, state, และ local financial legal requirements ตาม studying existing และ new legislation, enforcing adherence requirements, และ advising management needed actions. Prepares special financial reports ตาม collecting, analyzing, และ summarizing account information และ trends. Maintains customer confidence และ protects operations ตาม keeping financial information confidential. Maintains professional และ technical knowledge ตาม attending educational workshops; reดูing professional publications; establishing personal networks; participating ใน professional societies. Accomplishes result ตาม performing duty. Contributes team effort ตาม accomplishing related results เป็น needed."

